<item>
            <title>[LU-16550] edquot handling breaks testing</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16550</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4505&quot; title=&quot;invalid &amp;quot;Disk quota exceed&amp;quot; error&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4505&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4505&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; added a protecting against quota master flooding, but it seems to break number of quota tests.&lt;br/&gt;
for example, here is stats for sanity-quota over last few days:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
                     PASS FAIL TIMEOUT CRASH
sanity-quota         151  45   1       0      
sanity-quota         141  54   1       0      
sanity-quota         148  48   0       0      
sanity-quota         150  49   1       0      
sanity-quota         158  38   0       0      
sanity-quota         185  46   2       0      
sanity-quota         298  65   2       0      
sanity-quota         157  40   0       0      
sanity-quota         299  76   2       0
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;now with that check from &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4505&quot; title=&quot;invalid &amp;quot;Disk quota exceed&amp;quot; error&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4505&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4505&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; disabled:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;      
sanity-quota         71   4    0       0      
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the most frequest failure is 12b where the test sets inode limit to 2048, then wants to create 2048 files, but fails:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
Create 2048 files on mdt0...
running as uid/gid/euid/egid 60000/60000/60000/60000, groups:
 [createmany] [-m] [/mnt/lustre/d12b.sanity-quota/f12b.sanity-quota] [2048]
mknod(/mnt/lustre/d12b.sanity-quota/f12b.sanity-quota1024) error: Disk quota exceeded
total: 1024 create in 3.90 seconds: 262.27 ops/second
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
